<li id="cite_note-96"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-96">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">James 2:26; <a href="#CITEREFOstlingOstling2007">Ostling &amp; Ostling (2007</a>, p.&#160;336).</span>
